## Overview

MIRU is a small, independent app built by a single developer. This privacy policy explains how your data is handled, or more accurately, how it isn't.

## Data Collection

**We collect no data. None.**

MIRU does not collect, store, transmit, or process any personal information about you or your device. No analytics, no usage tracking, and no advertising identifiers.

## Third Parties

No data is shared with third parties because no data is collected in the first place. There are no third-party SDKs embedded for tracking or advertising purposes.

## Local Storage

Any data the app stores lives exclusively on your device. It never leaves your device and is never accessible to the developer.

